r Egypt before Jean-Philippe Mateta leveled with a late strike.\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 444, \"end\": 450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999979484073, \"rank\": 2.0515015127880297e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 525, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabre\", \"score\": 0.9999999999984084, \"rank\": 1.37657229848019e-12, \"text\": \"Saber\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabre\"}, {\"begin\": 559, \"end\": 564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3200574113052858e-14, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Philippe_Mateta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jean-Philippe Mateta\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Philippe_Mateta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Philippe_Mateta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mateta got a double before Michael Olise scored in extra time to earn Thierry Henry's side the victory and extend its quest for a second Olympic title in the final on Friday, August 9, at Parc des Princes against Spain, who earlier beat Morocco 2-1.\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Olise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michael Olise\