 secured a medal now but we have one more step to go to win our first football gold medal after 40 years.\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now Spain await us in the final and it's going to be a big game.\\\"\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1155, \"end\": 1160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999952252, \"rank\": 4.835256503662196e-12, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Egypt, which was playing its third Olympic semifinal, had more shots on goal during the first half before Saber opened the scoring in the 62nd minute, capitalizing on a rebound to power in a second attempt.\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1218, \"end\": 1223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3200574113052858e-14, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1324, \"end\": 1329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabre\", \"score\": 0.9999999999984084, \"rank\": 1.37657229848019e-12, \"text\": \"Saber\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France, which hit the woodwork three times throughout the match, equalized when Mateta finally found the net seven minutes from time from an Olise pass through Egypt's backline.\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1426, \"end\": 1432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999979484073, \"rank\": 2.0515015127880297e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1586, \"end\": 1591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3200574113052858e-14, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Egypt went down to 10 men early in extra time when Omar Fayed got a second yellow card for a foul on Desire Doue and it was dealt a further blow when Mateta scored again to put France ahead with a towering header in the 99th minute.\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3200574113052858e-14, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1656, \"end\": 1660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omar_Little\", \"score\": 0.7687297258117908, \"rank\": 0.2953042503974711, \"text\": \"Omar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omar_Little\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omar_Little\"}, {\"begin\": 1706, \"end\": 1712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Desire\", \"score\": 0.9999999997653504, \"rank\": 1.126164738936068e-10, \"text\": \"Desire\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Desire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Desire\"}, {\"begin\": 1713, \"end\": 1717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doue